inner text: WHEREAS Hadad Wanjie Philip (ID/0256937/63), is registered as proprietor in absolute ownership interest of all that piece of land situate in the district of Thika, registered under title number Ruiru/Ruiru East Block 2/197, and whereas sufficient evidence has been adduced to show that the land register (Green Card) of the said piece of land is missing, and whereas all efforts made to locate the said land register (Green Card) have failed, notice is given that after the expiration of sixty (60) days from the date hereof, provided no valid objection has been received within that period, I intend to open another land register and upon such opening the said missing land register shall be deemed obsolete and of no effect.
text:
GAZETTE NOTICE NO. 464 
THE LAND REGISTRATION ACT 
(No. 3 of 2012) 
LOSS OF LAND REGISTER 
WHEREAS Hadad Wanjie Philip (ID/0256937/63), is registered as proprietor in absolute ownership interest of all that piece of land situate in the district of Thika, registered under title No. Ruiru/Ruiru East Block 2/197, and whereas sufficient evidence has been adduced to show that the land register (Green Card) of the said piece of land is missing, and whereas all efforts made to locate the said land register (Green Card) have failed, notice is given that after the expiration of sixty (60) days from the date hereof, provided no valid objection has been received within that period, I intend to open another land register and upon such opening the said missing land register shall be deemed obsolete and of no effect. 
Dated the 20th January, 2017. 
B. K. LEITICH, 
MR/2694501 Land Registrar, Thika District.
